        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer167639223" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10850139954008908742">Carmela Ciuraru paints a fascinating picture of authors and their pseudonyms in <i>Nom de Plume</i>. This well-researched book contains detailed information about both well known and lesser known writers. More than a biography, you will discover why authors chose the names they did, as well as interesting facts about the personal and sometimes tragic events in their lives. You may look at literature differently after reading this enlightening collection of astonishing stories. I received this book free</span>
  <span id="freeText10850139954008908742" style="display:none">Carmela Ciuraru paints a fascinating picture of authors and their pseudonyms in <i>Nom de Plume</i>. This well-researched book contains detailed information about both well known and lesser known writers. More than a biography, you will discover why authors chose the names they did, as well as interesting facts about the personal and sometimes tragic events in their lives. You may look at literature differently after reading this enlightening collection of astonishing stories. I received this book free through Goodreads First Reads.</span>
