        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer225035292" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11388987918274614663">A history of authors and their pen names - from people seriously hiding their identities to authors just goofing off. It is really facinating how so many authors needed or were subsumed by the alternate identities. A light writing style kept the book moving along, but by the end it really had me thinking.</span>

          </span>
